seway</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale_road\" title=\"Duskendale road\">Duskendale road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Goldroad\" title=\"Goldroad\">Goldroad</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_road\" title=\"High road\">High road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">Kingsroad</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ocean_road\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ocean road\">Ocean road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Prince%27s_Pass\" title=\"Prince&#39;s Pass\">Prince's Pass</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/River_road\" title=\"River road\">River road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rosby_road\" title=\"Rosby road\">Rosby road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roseroad\" title=\"Roseroad\">Roseroad</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/West_way\" title=\"West way\">West way</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Godsway</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sand_Road\" title=\"Sand Road\">Sand Road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Silk_Road\" title=\"Silk Road\">Silk Road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Steel_Road\" title=\"Steel Road\">Steel Road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Road\" title=\"Stone Road\">Stone Road</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_roads\" title=\"Valyrian roads\">Valyrian roads</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Demon_road\" title=\"Demon road\">Demon road</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Sothoryos\" title=\"Sothoryos\">Sothoryos</a></td><td style=\"text-align:l